metadata.name: Modern Royalty
metadata.description:
"Modern Royalty" is a dynamic art piece that reimagines the concept of royalty in a contemporary light.  
I use bold strokes and rich colors to showcase the regal splendor and grace of modern royalty. The subject is depicted with a blend of classical elements and modern aesthetics, creating a unique and eye-catching depiction of royalty. The textured details and vivid colors add depth and dimension to the piece, making it a visually stunning tribute to the enduring beauty of royalty.
